profile: Bronson Johnson Seamless Eavestroughs has quickly become one of Ottawa's top choices for your water evacuation requirements!  We specialize in Eavestrough (Gutter) installation.  BJSE also provides Leaf Screen (Leaf Guard) protection.  We have exclusive rights to GT Premium Micro Leaf Screen which is ideal for metal roofing systems.   Our mission is to be Referred by our Customers, Revered by our Competitors and Respected by our Community.
products: We only use 0.032" thick 5 inch Seamless Eavestrough; Exclusive rights to the Hidden Hanger used in our installations; Leaf Guard, Leaf Screen; Environmentally friendly Rain Barrel installation.  Also, ask about our product that eliminates  "Tiger Stripes" which occur on white and light coloured eaves.

specialities: B.J.S.E is the only company in Ottawa to specialize in the installation of.032" thick Aluminum Eavestroughs which is significantly stronger than standard .023", .024" and .027" material used by our competitors. profile:
At Excel Building & Roofing we are "On top of what matters most" with specialties in residential and commercial roofing and renovations in the Ottawa and surrounding area. As an Ottawa contractor we deliver the best in quality, workmanship and insist the job is done right the first time. 

With all the chaos that comes with our day to day lives we know that any home project, needed or wanted, can seem both overwhelming and out of reach. At Excel Building & Roofing we are with you every step of the way.

Our team has over 25 years combined experience in the field and we are extremely motivated to make a change in the way this city views the construction industry. "A lot of companies are faceless and in it for a quick buck. This isn't just a "job" for us and our clients are not just "another project", this is how we make our living and support our family." 

Call us picky, but quality is a prerequisite and a bad job is simply unacceptable. We do not rush jobs and choose our materials and team very carefully to ensure it is done right the first time.

When you choose Excel you receive:
- A Green Company, we recycle 100% of materials removed from your home.
- Superior quality and workmanship   
- Always above standard materials and installation
- Constant management - during and after installation inspections 
- No hidden fees or extras, what we quote you is what you pay.

*** Ottawa Roofing experts***

profile:
MARKELANGELO'S ROOFING serves the greater Ottawa area.  We are a professional and trustworthy company with a proven track record. We have fully trained, certified employees who specialize in specific installation procedures and focus 100% on quality control to ensure your satisfaction with the final product. 
 
As a testament to our exceptional level of service, our clients eagerly recommend us to friends and family. In fact, we built Markelangelo’s solely through word of mouth.

We are very aware of how our business impacts the environment. We contribute by participating in recycling programs available at local landfills. All garbage, shingles, metal and wood are separated before we take our dump trailers to these landfills. Each waste product is then put into its appropriate area of the landfill and processed. We save approximately a thousand tonnes of material being buried in landfills every year.

profile:
Rest Assured Roofing specializes in asphalt shingled roof removals and new roof installations. Our goal is to provide homeowners with an incredible experience from the moment they get in touch with us, to the final clean-up.

We offer an industry-leading, 10-year workmanship warranty that has helped us provide properties with an extensive range of roofing services such as residential roofing Ottawa, Emergency roof repair, guaranteeing excellent customer satisfaction. To extend the longevity of your roof, we utilize the highest quality material to ensure that you receive an incredible, and efficient roofing experience.

Fully Insured
Qualified in Certainteed installations as well as products
48-Hour Estimate Guarantee
24/7 Emergency Service

WARRANTY INFORMATION: 
We have passed both written testing and quality inspections to become certified with Certainteed. This allows us to provide our customers with an extended 50 year Surestart warrantee. What does that mean?
Well, SureStart offers the best coverage you can get on your  new roof and here is what it provides:

- 100% of materials:
All shingles required to repair or replace the defective product will be provided free. No exceptions.

- 100% of labor:
All labor required to repair defective shingles or apply new shingles to replace the defective shingles will be paid by CertainTeed, based on local fair market value for labor.

- Additional costs:
The cost of flashing, metal work, tear-off and disposal are included.

- Without prorating the costs: 
The cost of materials and labor are not prorated or otherwise reduced.

profile:
Colson Roofing Inc. is a local contractor specializing in flat and shingle re-roofing, skylight and sun tunnel installations, new construction and roof repairs.  We have over 19 years of experience and feel as though we have taken waterproofing to the next level.  We complete each job with dedication and professionalism and are not satisfied until you are.  We are certified by the manufacturer for flat roofs, shingle roofs, skylights and sun tunnels.

​Servicing Ottawa East, Ottawa Centre & Ottawa South with complete roofing services, we guarantee top quality workmanship, honesty and reliability.  At Colson Roofing we do NOT sub-contract, are fully WSIB compliant, and provide full written workmanship warranties.  We are fully insured, BBB accredited A+, waterproofing specialists.  

We strive for excellence while using today's most innovative and advanced waterproofing techniques, to ensure complete protection for your home against inclement weather.  We are certified and experienced with all safety procedures, and take pride in all of our installations.  We honor all of our warranties and have very high standards for customer satisfaction.

profile:
The owner of B.H Roofing has been in business for 30 years. We've completed thousands of jobs in Ottawa and surrounding area. B.H Roofing has been a family owned and run business since its founding. We take pride in our work, ensure quality and our trademark is to leave the property spotless.

Our goal is to build strong and long lasting relationships with our customers. We guarantee our work and will be there for you long after the job is done. The thousands of satisfied customers we've served will attest to this.

Choosing a roofing company can be stressful. Beware of companies who outsource / subcontract their work or who use piece work payment. This practice tends to encourage shortcuts and mistakes by employees resulting in long term roof problems. We do not subcontract and we pay our employees by the hour. They take the time to ensure the job is done properly and the cleanup is meticulous.

profile:
Certain Seal Roofing is an Ottawa roofing company, based in east Ottawa. We offer a variety of roofing, roof repair and siding services to the greater Ottawa Region: Stittsville, Kanata, Bells Corners, Richmond, Nepean, Barrhaven, Riverside South, Manotick, Greely, Metcalfe, Edwards, Sandy Hill, Glebe, Downtown Ottawa, Rothwell Heights, Vanier, Gloucester, Greenboro, Hunt Club, Blackburn Hamlet, Orleans, Navan, Clarence Rockland, Prescott Russell, Emrbun, Vars, Sarsfield, Limoges, Carlsbad Springs, Kars Osgoode, Wendover and Hammond.

Our professional installers have decades of combined experience servicing roofs in the Ottawa area, and we are proud to say that this will be our 5th year operating in the Ottawa roofing industry. Ottawa has a large variety of roofing contractors to choose from and we find for many customers it comes down to a matter of quality, of course, but also price. With Certain Seal Roofing you can get the best of both we offer quality craftsmanship at an affordable price. So, if you are looking for an Ottawa roofing company that is dedicated to providing excellent service and quality craftsmanship at an affordable rate please give us a call for a free estimate, (613)913-2199. 

Whether you need a new roof, re-roof, or small repair, we are committed to making sure that every customer is completely satisfied that they have hired the proper professional to do their roofing work. In short, we offer a very high caliber of quality and service at a competitive price. We are dedicated to creating a long-lasting reputation in the community as a top quality roofer, with regards to both our end-product and our customer service

Our team of highly trained roofers is equipped with the latest tools and materials to ensure that every job we carry out is done right. While we are known for our work with asphalt shingle roofs, we also have extensive expertise in working with metal roofs and all metal roofing systems.We have been proudly serving clients for over 25 years. Our certified and professional staff will take the time to walk you through each step of your roofing job, from start to finish. T.A.R Roofing was created by Mr. Paul-André Côté with more than 15 years of experience in the foeld of new, residential and commercial roofs. With a burning desire and a dream of becoming a reference in the field of roofing, he was able to make himself known quickly by the quality of his work and the recognition of his clients. Constantly innovating from years to years, Mr. Côté gained a great reputation by giving more to his customers. Paul-André opts for an exceptional and quality service, a perfect cleaning of the workplaces and a remarkable after-sales service in order to satisfy his customers and to give them great advice.
